summary: Egg hatching has been very slow lately, I’ve just been busy w/ non-pokemon activities, but I have been poking away at it here...
caption:
Egg hatching has been very slow lately, I’ve just been busy w/ non-pokemon activities, but I have been poking away at it here and there, and yesterday this handsome green borb popped out.

No moon ball of course, but even so I’m quite thrilled. For a nickname, I’m leaning towards ‘Archimedes’, after the owl in Disney’s Sword in the Stone, but I’m not 100% committed yet, so any suggestions are more than welcome.
